{"tha-ap4:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap4:0.2":"Buddhavagga ","tha-ap4:0.3":"Mahamoggallanattheraapadana ","tha-ap4:1.1":"“Anomadassi bhagava, ","tha-ap4:1.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap4:1.3":"Vihasi himavantamhi, ","tha-ap4:1.4":"devasanghapurakkhato. ","tha-ap4:2.1":"Varuno nama namena, ","tha-ap4:2.2":"nagaraja aham tada; ","tha-ap4:2.3":"Kamarupi vikubbami, ","tha-ap4:2.4":"mahodadhinivasaham. ","tha-ap4:3.1":"Sanganiyam ganam hitva, ","tha-ap4:3.2":"turiyam patthapesaham; ","tha-ap4:3.3":"Sambuddham parivaretva, ","tha-ap4:3.4":"vadesum acchara tada. ","tha-ap4:4.1":"Vajjamanesu turesu, ","tha-ap4:4.2":"deva turani vajjayum; ","tha-ap4:4.3":"Ubhinnam saddam sutvana, ","tha-ap4:4.4":"buddhopi sampabujjhatha. ","tha-ap4:5.1":"Nimantetvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap4:5.2":"sakam bhavanupagamim; ","tha-ap4:5.3":"Asanam pannapetvana, ","tha-ap4:5.4":"kalamarocayim aham. ","tha-ap4:6.1":"Khinasavasahassehi, ","tha-ap4:6.2":"parivuto lokanayako; ","tha-ap4:6.3":"Obhasento disa sabba, ","tha-ap4:6.4":"bhavanam me upagami. ","tha-ap4:7.1":"Upavittham mahaviram, ","tha-ap4:7.2":"Devadevam narasabham; ","tha-ap4:7.3":"Sabhikkhusangham tappesim, ","tha-ap4:7.4":"Annapanenaham tada. ","tha-ap4:8.1":"Anumodi mahaviro, ","tha-ap4:8.2":"sayambhu aggapuggalo; ","tha-ap4:8.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap4:8.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap4:9.1":"Yo so sangham apujesi, ","tha-ap4:9.2":"buddhanca lokanayakam; ","tha-ap4:9.3":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap4:9.4":"devalokam gamissati. ","tha-ap4:10.1":"Sattasattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap4:10.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap4:10.3":"Pathabya rajjam atthasatam, ","tha-ap4:10.4":"vasudham avasissati. ","tha-ap4:11.1":"Pancapannasakkhattunca, ","tha-ap4:11.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap4:11.3":"Bhoga asankhiya tassa, ","tha-ap4:11.4":"uppajjissanti tavade. ","tha-ap4:12.1":"Aparimeyye ito kappe, ","tha-ap4:12.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap4:12.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap4:12.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap4:13.1":"Niraya so cavitvana, ","tha-ap4:13.2":"manussatam gamissati; ","tha-ap4:13.3":"Kolito nama namena, ","tha-ap4:13.4":"brahmabandhu bhavissati. ","tha-ap4:14.1":"So paccha pabbajitvana, ","tha-ap4:14.2":"kusalamulena codito; ","tha-ap4:14.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap4:14.4":"dutiyo hessati savako. ","tha-ap4:15.1":"Araddhaviriyo pahitatto, ","tha-ap4:15.2":"Iddhiya paramim gato; ","tha-ap4:15.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap4:15.4":"Nibbayissatinasavo. ","tha-ap4:16.1":"Papamittopanissaya, ","tha-ap4:16.2":"kamaragavasam gato; ","tha-ap4:16.3":"Mataram pitarancapi, ","tha-ap4:16.4":"ghatayim dutthamanaso. ","tha-ap4:17.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap4:17.2":"nirayam atha manusam; ","tha-ap4:17.3":"Papakammasamangita, ","tha-ap4:17.4":"bhinnasiso maramaham. ","tha-ap4:18.1":"Idam pacchimakam mayham, ","tha-ap4:18.2":"carimo vattate bhavo; ","tha-ap4:18.3":"Idhapi ediso mayham, ","tha-ap4:18.4":"maranakale bhavissati. ","tha-ap4:19.1":"Pavivekamanuyutto, ","tha-ap4:19.2":"samadhibhavanarato; ","tha-ap4:19.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap4:19.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap4:20.1":"Dharanimpi sugambhiram, ","tha-ap4:20.2":"bahalam duppadhamsiyam; ","tha-ap4:20.3":"Vamangutthena khobheyyam, ","tha-ap4:20.4":"iddhiya paramim gato. ","tha-ap4:21.1":"Asmimanam na passami, ","tha-ap4:21.2":"mano mayham na vijjati; ","tha-ap4:21.3":"Samanere upadaya, ","tha-ap4:21.4":"garucittam karomaham. ","tha-ap4:22.1":"Aparimeyye ito kappe, ","tha-ap4:22.2":"yam kammamabhiniharim; ","tha-ap4:22.3":"Taham bhumimanuppatto, ","tha-ap4:22.4":"pattomhi asavakkhayam. ","tha-ap4:23.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap4:23.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap4:23.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap4:23.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap4:24.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma mahamoggallano thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap4:25.1":"Mahamoggallanattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}